    "Html": "\r\n<p>One problem/question: The project runs fine, however, if at runtime I change Pedro&rsquo;s name to Alejandro (by editing Pedro&rsquo;s name in the &ldquo;Name&rdquo; column&rdquo;) the control remains a button and does not change to a TextBlock. Put otherwise,\r\n TemplateSelector.SelectTemplate() is not being called when data is edited.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You can, however, force the change by sorting on a column after changing Pedro&rsquo;s name, and then suddenly the Button goes away and is replaced by a TextBlock, as we would expect. But, why can&rsquo;t we have the DataTemplate switched as soon as Pedro&rsquo;s\r\n name is changed?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Jerimiah&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
